Day 4 (Export Activity Logs and Explore KQL)
•	Exported Azure Subscription Activity Logs to monitor administrative and resource-level actions within the environment.
•	Loaded training data from the Microsoft Sentinel Training Lab solution to simulate security events.
•	Began exploring KQL (Kusto Query Language) for querying logs, focusing on detecting failed logins and authentication activity

