Day 5 (Create Microsoft Sentinel Dashboard)
•	Created a custom Microsoft Sentinel dashboard to visualize key security metrics and insights from ingested data.
•	Added widgets for failed logons, authentication trends, and alert summaries to enhance real-time visibility into security events.
•	Customized layout and filters to support faster incident triage and analysis.

