Sentinel dashboard and visualization panels


Day 6 (Connect Microsoft Defender XDR and Create Analytic Rule)
•	Connected Microsoft Defender XDR to Microsoft Sentinel to unify threat data and enhance detection capabilities across endpoints and cloud workloads.
•	Created a custom analytic rule in Sentinel using sample log data to simulate and detect brute-force attack patterns.
•	Tested the rule’s trigger logic and verified alert generation in the Sentinel incident’s view.
Screenshots
 
XDR connector setup

 
Analytic rule creation

 
